    <section id="id15883387">
      <title>Learning Objectives</title>
      <para id="id15842040">With 100% accuracy during a: memory building activity, exercises, lab assignment, problems, or timed quiz/exam; the student is expected to:</para>
      <list id="id16814888" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>Define the terms on the definitions as listed in the modules associated with this chapter.</item>
        <item>Identify which selection control structures are commonly used a counting loops.</item>
        <item>Be able to write pseudo code or flowcharting for the for control structure.</item>
        <item>Be able to write C++ source code for a for control structure.</item>
        <item>When feasible, be able to convert C++ source code from while loop acting like a counting loop to a for loop and and vice versa.</item>
      </list>
    </section>
